{"tid":330012,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"啲人有幾冇教養先可以攞酒店房既熱水煲黎整野食","createTime":"2017-07-20T22:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T02:56:14.000Z","uid":91835,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c744746fc87b0b48608d8a3efb8c48e2329c5fe8","tid":330012,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:57:42.000Z","msg":"熱水煲既function都唔識？<br />\n熱水煲係for煲熱水，唔係俾人放啲食物入去煮<br />\n想食杯麵既就買個杯麵，然後用煲熱既水淥<br />\n而唔係倒個麵入熱水煲度煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢啲咁有創意既人又唔見佢將屋企個電熱水煲咁樣用喎<br />\n屋企既電熱水煲係電熱水煲，酒店既就唔係？<br />\n酒店果啲唔係自己財物，所以鍾意點用都得？<br />\n有冇諗過負責清潔熱水煲果位同事，<br />\n有冇諗過下一手住客用既時候俾人整污糟哂？<br />\n唉，香港人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa83b51ddbb5782b304d8451017b7e5988a32d14","tid":330012,"uid":24989,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:08:59.000Z","msg":"樓主係清潔工"},{"pid":"1a5cb22d984b9188db65a75c7b3b323fe36df9d8","tid":330012,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:10:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa78489e36c4b84753329b8a8f7c5eda16c8d6c8","tid":330012,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:16:18.000Z","msg":"有人用黎"},{"pid":"25585ed23883d0d71a0109476fa3baedc996a9e1","tid":330012,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:17:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"822478d286e89519133c72b41f63b20ad1c60c2a","tid":330012,"uid":1333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:17:07.000Z","msg":"有人用黎嘔，垃圾桶，放尿play <br />\n你真係想用？"},{"pid":"9b687fbd6b9cdb3d2aac7ff6f7501130009a903f","tid":330012,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:18:16.000Z","msg":"所以唔會用 除非真係好肚餓要食杯麵<br />\n就算用都會煲兩三轉倒左佢先用"},{"pid":"55eb4c64c16889f80ab57acc127877903e110563","tid":330012,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike